{"tid":1837284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗暴之戰】受害市民去信警務處追討損失 反遭投訴課致電恐嚇藏彈殼","createTime":"2020-01-23T14:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T09:48:44.000Z","uid":41998,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd43f2aaf9cdb956daae61d87e6f227ccd6ac5f","tid":1837284,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:25:02.000Z","msg":"警暴肆虐，至今未曾有一句道歉，遑論回應追討個人損失的受害市民。去年尾多人在尖沙嘴清真寺外被警方水炮車以藍色水劑射中、有沙田住戶窗口玻璃亦被警方的催淚彈射爆，兩宗事件的受害者均透過律師去信警務處，至今都無回覆。涉事沙田住戶認為警方態度被動，「好似唔想幫我哋咁」，更曾收到投訴警察課致電，恐嚇她違法藏有彈殼，「叫你嚟執又唔執，又調返轉話我犯法。」<br />\n<br />\n去年10月中警方曾出動水炮車射向尖沙嘴清真寺，多人被藍色水劑射中，其中一名受害者張小姐連續一周腹瀉，至今出席遊行活動，若聞到催淚氣體仍會腹瀉。另一名受害人、從事少數族裔工作的張小姐亦指，被射中後個人「懵懵哋」，醫生指疑為腦震盪。第三位受害人、巴裔商人簡浩名批評政府只向權貴道歉，「唔通我哋唔係人咩？唔值得你道歉？」<br />\n<br />\n三人的代表律師陳惠源11月中去信警務處，提出47條問題，要求警方公開藍色水劑成份、當時的執法標準等，惟至今仍無回覆。陳惠源批評警方拒絕公開成份，等同拒絕向被藍色水劑射中的市民提供醫療協助，「唔知成份醫生都唔知點醫」，他質疑警方是要毒殺市民。陳惠源更指，去信查詢後警方竟反問他「有咩法律理據問咁多問題」，令他感到氣憤，「點解我哋納稅人要俾你兇？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年11月中警方在沙田市中心驅散示威者時，一枚催淚彈射爆5樓住戶窗口玻璃，並於屋內爆開。住戶鄭太表示，事隔至今已超過兩個月，她曾向投訴警察課投訴，並向警務處發律師信，惟她認為警察態度被動，「好似唔想幫我哋咁。」鄭太指，催淚彈射中屋後，<span style=\"color: red;\">她曾兩度向警務處發信，要度警方上門撿走彈殼，一直未獲回應，其後卻收到投訴警察課致電，恐嚇她若單位內仍藏有彈殼即屬違法，鄭太表示十分無奈，「叫你嚟執又唔執，又調返轉話我犯法。」</span><br />\n<br />\n直至昨日（22日），鄭太方收到律政司回信，指警方將於明日上門檢走彈殼。鄭太指，不敢再住在好運中心單位，「我唔知個單位會唔會已經被污染咗」，曾去信警務處要求派出專家檢測單位內的空氣質素遭拒，這兩個月來要納空租，更另找住所，向警方要求賠償，至今都無回覆。鄭太的代表律師陳惠源指，鄭太不會放棄追究，「唔單只係金錢上嘅損失，仲有精神上嘅壓力同損失都要繼續做。」<br />\n跟進上述兩宗個案的公民黨立法會議員楊岳橋表示，警方至今「一句道歉都冇」，批評政府置人命及港人尊嚴於不顧。譚文豪亦指，警方近半年來的行動讓市民對體制完全失去信心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200123/NQP5WDG6NWZEJMQF5BFTO65FLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200123%2FNQP5WDG6NWZEJMQF5BFTO65FLM%2F&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=6862511d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200123%2FNQP5WDG6NWZEJMQF5BFTO65FLM%2F&h=7f8889de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200123/NQP5WDG6NWZEJMQF5BFTO65FLM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c80QbXu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc80QbXu.jpg&h=ad49bc5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06jJwXv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06jJwXv.jpg&h=1856e204&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a144f9dbba55139a3fbc88c04bb5b6db59333dd6","tid":1837284,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:28:44.000Z","msg":"淨係識嚇鳩人，嘢又唔撚做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7663c0ffd2230156b3145e53f3e012a5332a1066","tid":1837284,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d92f8d78d7b26ad3448c3f8bc77efddd0da2d6","tid":1837284,"uid":116545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:30:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3777340cc103d15c157ad2fdfa2481629f8e7e6f","tid":1837284,"uid":277888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:31:41.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168eb4cee1fe30148b03ad1133c99492c0c0e111","tid":1837284,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"［行動］文宣向有意到港醫病嘅武漢肺炎病人，引導佢地搵香港警署求助<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837289</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"95ca8a6d01137ff6a7399637237afc7068fac867","tid":1837284,"uid":41998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"黑警fb咁鍾意出嚟澄清乜乜柒柒，呢單係咪駁唔到啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1dfdf0995a7a099bde33cfd30a56660415da26","tid":1837284,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:32:24.000Z","msg":"呢啲都算係警暴啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暴係包括埋言語上嘅暴力"},{"pid":"22879c4dd584782cfcad6ebb449ab5415a447e25","tid":1837284,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:32:51.000Z","msg":"狗閪黎"},{"pid":"8aac976ed70aac62e5e650eeb480a85e0e56490a","tid":1837284,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b1dfdf0995a7a099bde33cfd30a56660415da26","tid":1837284,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:32:24.000Z","msg":"呢啲都算係警暴啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暴係包括埋言語上嘅暴力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:35:11.000Z","msg":"但「睇」唔到啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2d956b015b4bd6bee71f826ba7ed0d4c8aa614","tid":1837284,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:42:04.000Z","msg":"告到上法座<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死黑警"},{"pid":"9624a7a6a6b700ac4e20bcbc4a4f54ed22ddba4b","tid":1837284,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7697eade935d32339d36b8cbd334d5ed9077c226","tid":1837284,"uid":68779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559c4027dfd92da3de8b70d188b848671cb30ce7","tid":1837284,"uid